        [
          "You used to be a profesional kidnapper, making people disappear and then returning them for the appropriate fee.  Now you are making vampires disappear - come of them get returned, and some of them permanently vanish in the depths of your Master's hold.  Your rather fond of your new abilities, though the loss of freedom bother yhou from time to time.  You liked being an independent agent, and you are still pulling the odd independent job to keep your hadn in.",
